# --- Authentication ---
#
# For CI / automated runs, use an App Store Connect API key instead of
# Apple ID credentials. Generate one at:
#   https://appstoreconnect.apple.com/access/integrations/api
#
# Then either:
#   1. Set the FASTLANE_API_KEY_PATH env var pointing to the .json key file, or
#   2. Pass it in the Fastfile via app_store_connect_api_key()
#
# For local runs, Fastlane will prompt for Apple ID if no API key is set.
